  <brief_title>MAXOMAT ® in the Treatment of Severe Early Onset Intrauterine Growth Retardation on Pre-pubertal Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Cohort of Pre-pubertal Children for the Study of Optimization of Methods of Administration of the Biosynthetic Growth Hormone MAXOMAT ® in the Treatment of Severe Early Onset Intrauterine Growth Retardation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
