  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Pre-pubertal children of either sex presenting with severe early onset intrauterine
             growth retardation (I.U.G.R.)

          -  Height Less Than or Equal to -3 SD

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Age less than 3 years

        The above information is not intended to contain all considerations relevant to a patient's
        potential participation in a clinical trial.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
